  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><em>You touch a bit of bloodhound fur to your nose, heightening your senses and projecting your awareness outside of your body. You can smell a plant or animal of your choice in your vicinity.</em></p><p><strong>Ritual Casting Time:</strong> 1 Minute</p><p><strong>Utility Spell</strong></p><p>Describe or name a specific kind of &amp;reference[beast] or &amp;reference[plant]. You don't need line of sight to the target.</p><ul><li><p>You learn the direction and distance to the closest creature or plant of that kind within 5 miles, if any are present.</p></li><li><p>If the creature is in motion, you know the direction of its movement.</p></li></ul></div><p></p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><strong>*Upcasting</strong>: Range increases by 5 miles for each spell level above 2nd.</p></div>",
      "chat": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><strong>Ritual Casting Time:</strong> 10 Minutes</p><p><strong>Utility Spell</strong></p><p>Describe or name a specific kind of &amp;reference[beast] or &amp;reference[plant]. You don't need line of sight to the target.</p><ul><li><p>You learn the direction and distance to the closest creature or plant of that kind within 5 miles, if any are present.</p></li><li><p>If the creature is in motion, you know the direction of its movement.</p></li></ul></div><p></p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Signika, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\">*</strong></span><strong>Upcasting</strong>: Range increases by 5 miles for each spell level above 2nd.</p></div>"
